
flowchart TB
    A[Decision Space]

    A --> B[Low Defensibility]
    A --> C[Balanced Zone]
    A --> D[High Defensibility]

    B --> B1[Fast Decisions]
    B1 --> B2[Higher Risk]

    C --> C1[Evidence‑based Tradeoffs]
    C1 --> C2[Meaningful Outcomes]

    D --> D1[Slow Decisions]
    D1 --> D2[Approval Theater]
    D2 --> D3[Underwhelming Outcomes]

    style C fill:#e8ffe8,stroke:#2d7a2d,stroke-width:2px
    style D fill:#ffe6e6,stroke:#b20000